♪ So you got to let me know

1:28:14.985 --> 1:28:18.336
♪ Should I stay
or should I go? ♪

1:28:19.511 --> 1:28:26.388
♪ It's always
tease, tease, tease ♪

1:28:26.431 --> 1:28:31.480
♪ You're happy
when I'm on my knees ♪

1:28:31.523 --> 1:28:36.223
♪ One day it's fine,
